data.description: Great tucked away 18.99 Acre Property! 15 irrigated acres currently in Grass/ Alfalfa, completely fenced with 8' game fencing and flood irrigated with 6" and 8" gated pipe. 27' Dbl. gate for easy access.  Cross fenced for rotational grazing in separate pastures. Three bedroom, two bath home with 1200 sqft of living space. Two by six framing throughout for an extra insulated home. Stay warm in the winter and cool in the summer for a fraction of the cost. This home has been recently remodeled with lifetime waterproof vinyl flooring throughout house, new hot water heater and pressure valve, new fan in the bathroom, new vanity and toilet . Electric forced air and wood stove for heat, evaporative cooler for air conditioning. 1/3 ownership shared well for the 5 zone automatic sprinkler system. Drip zones in flower beds. Enjoy your own fruit from two apricot trees, two apple trees, one peach tree, one cherry tree and four black walnut trees.
